Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Product
    The Product class is a container for information representing a product.
    WalmartCrawler
    The WalmartCrawler is an application which scrapes information from the walmart.com database using a url representing a site search.
    WalmartRequest
    The Walmart request builds the walmart.com url to search for products defined by the query list and page number
    WalmartResponse
    The WalmartResponse class builds a list of Products from the HtmlPage associated with it, and contains information on how many results occured on the WalmartRequest search parameters.
    WebRequest
    Abstract class for a WebRequest.
    WebResponse
    Abstract class for a WebResponse.
    WebServiceClient
    The WebServiceClient contains methods to process WebRequests and return the relative WebResponses.
